        <h1>About SK Jewelry</h1>
        
        <section class="about-content">
            <img src="workshop.jpg" alt="SK Jewelry Workshop" class="about-image">
            <p>SK Jewelry is a passionate artisan workshop based in Alexandria, Egypt. We specialize in creating unique, handcrafted jewelry inspired by the rich history and intricate designs of ancient Egyptian culture.</p>
            
            <p>Our founder, Sarah Kamel, started this journey with a deep love for both jewelry making and Egyptology. Combining these passions, she created SK Jewelry to bring the mystique and elegance of pharaonic designs to modern-day fashion enthusiasts.</p>
            
            <p>Each piece in our collection is meticulously crafted using traditional techniques and high-quality materials. We pride ourselves on attention to detail and historical accuracy, ensuring that every item tells a story from Egypt's glorious past.</p>
            
            <p>At SK Jewelry, we believe in preserving cultural heritage while creating contemporary pieces that resonate with today's fashion-forward individuals. Our goal is to offer not just jewelry, but wearable art that connects you to the timeless beauty of ancient Egypt.</p>
        </section>
